{"id":161592,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011615/","date":"2011-06-16T03:30:15Z","modified":"2011-06-16T03:30:15Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/6/15","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8576472/British-artist-Anish-Kapoor-cancels-China-show-over-Ai-Weiwei-detention.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国艺术家取消到中国的展览以抗议艾未未被关押</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3553\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">威尼斯双年展上的艾未未</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——关于艾未未的一条标语引起不同的解读</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/15/opinion/15friedman.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“正义”走向世界</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“哈佛教授桑德尔的教学在中国既令人耳目一新，又有现实意义”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110615/ap_en_ot/as_china_vargas_llosa;_ylt=AhZINS5OmXQeSbhXn2F7GVdxFb8C;_ylu=X3oDMTJtMTFvN2RzBGFzc2V0A2FwLzIwMTEwNjE1L2FzX2NoaW5hX3Zhcmdhc19sbG9zYQRjcG9zAzEEcG9zAzEEc2VjA3luX3RvcF9zdG9yeQRzbGsDaW5jaGluYXZhcmdh\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">诺贝尔文学奖得主略萨在中国批评专制政权</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“独裁与专制政府会使得全社会变得腐败”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/16/world/asia/16iht-letter16.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国高层缺乏安全感</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“他们自认为把国家治理得很好，因此不理解为什么人民并不爱戴他们”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲哨兵</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3253&#038;Itemid=173\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缺乏特色的香港特首候选人</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“北京当局选择下一任香港特首时，最不看重的就是领导能力”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/06/15/monroe-doctrines-in-asia/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲的门罗主义？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国正在推行亚洲版的门罗主义，想把美国赶出西太平洋，自立为地区霸权”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">快公司</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.fastcompany.com/1758927/how-chinas-cellphone-pirates-are-toppling-governments-in-india-and-the-middle-east\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国山寨手机摧毁中东国家的政府</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——廉价手机使信息随处可得，在中东（还有中国）带来意料之外的后果</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304259304576373391101828876.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对美国的网络攻击</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“北京正在成功盗取研发成果、软件代码、技术诀窍和政府计划”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110615/ap_on_re_as/as_china_lead_poisoning\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对铅中毒疫情三缄其口</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“人权观察”组织发布报告，称中国数百万儿童患铅中毒，而地方官员试图掩盖真相</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/jun/15/pollution-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">也有报道）</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110614/wl_nm/us_myanmar_china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缅甸边境地区难民逃入中国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国援助缅甸建设太平河水坝，引起当地克钦族与政府之间的冲突”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-15/huntsman-money-made-in-china-tests-obama-envoy-s-2012-hopes.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">洪博培家族在中国的发财史将对他的竞选带来考验</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——其家族公司在中国的收入在他出任大使期间增长了</span><span>57%</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯研究所</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/testimony/2011/0615_china_economic_development_prasad.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的经济发展和工业政策方针</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“政府的难题在于战胜利益集团的阻挠，继续实施改革，实现十二五规划”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/kenrapoza/2011/06/14/accounting-scandals-galore-china-not-enron-bound/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">虽然上市公司财务问题突出，</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">但</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国并非安然公司</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“如果你认为可以完全依靠审计，那你是在自欺欺人”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3535\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的水资源挑战</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——环境历史学家</span><span><span>Ken Pomeranz</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">答问</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g3BazP3Jmb2sDYyKgZKfI-tc5K8A?docId=3326b04205ba47998bcc1ab532687ede\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称国内核电站全部通过检查</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“能源需求型的经济发展，使得中国必须扩大核电规模”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/16/business/energy-environment/16green.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对能源效率重燃兴趣</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——住宅建设的高速发展带来用电需求激增，中国试图通过政策倾斜鼓励提高能源使用效率</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2077693,00.html?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么中国妈妈想到美国来生孩子</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“选择这条路，不仅要承担出生和产后的费用，还要付出很多的后续代价”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>MSNBC – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/06/15/6854190-reconstruction-slow-in-tibetan-town\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">玉树的重建工作进展缓慢</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“在中国，这是我第一次见到一座没有塔吊的城市”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京烤鸭</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.pekingduck.org/2011/06/socrates-in-sichuan-by-peter-j-vernezze/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">书评：《苏格拉底在四川》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国学生本能地想要给出中庸的答案，他们不想伤任何人的面子”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br /></span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-7873146662197640610?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":777,"categories":[1],"tags":[13232]}